   313→   *
   314→   * Public method to allow custom Gmail API operations with built-in retry logic.
   315→   * Automatically retries on rate limit errors (429) with exponential backoff.
   316→   *
   317→   * @param operation - Async operation to execute
   318→   * @param options - Retry options
   319→   * @returns Operation result
   320→   * @throws Error if all retry attempts fail
   321→   * @public
   322→   */
   323→  async executeWithRetry<T>(operation: () => Promise<T>, options?: GmailRequestOptions): Promise<T> {
   324→    const maxRetries = options?.maxRetries ?? 3;
   325→    const retryDelayMs = options?.retryDelayMs ?? 1000;
   326→    const retryOnRateLimit = options?.retryOnRateLimit ?? false;
   327→
